asset_contract.name: Kumo x World
asset_contract.description:
Female founder and creator of 6,666 Kumo residents, 9 classes, 500+ traits.

A percentage of sales go towards childrens and mental health charities

Our roadmap includes Children Storybooks, Kumochis (like pets) for evolving, KxW Coins and future game development.
Come join us on our adventures and write the story of Kumo's World with us.
